OL,3,CJLR worker who killed boy, 12, in hit-
OL,4,Cand-run changes plea to guilty
OL,6,FA Jaguar Land Rover worker charged
OL,7,Fwith causing death by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving in a hit-and-run in Birmingham
OL,9,Fwhich a 12-year old schoolboy died,
OL,10,Fhas changed his plea to guilty.
OL,12,FAzaan Khan was killed as he rode his
OL,13,Fbike home from school on the 8th June
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FHe had been to a shop with two friends
OL,17,Fand was crossing Coventry Road in
OL,18,FSouth Yardley at the time.
OL,20,FAzaan received a blood transfusion but
OL,21,Fdied at the scene.
