OL,6,FShazad Alam, who is 33 and from
OL,7,FSheldon, was arrested and charged with
OL,8,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,10,FHaving previously pleaded not guilty,
OL,11,FShazad Alam changed that plea at
OL,12,FBirmingham Crown Court today,
OL,13,Faccepting the charge of causing death
OL,14,Fby dangerous driving.
OL,16,FIn a hearing that lasted a few
OL,17,Fminutes, Shazad Alam spoke only to
OL,18,Fconfirm his name and state his plea of
OL,19,Fguilty.
OL,21,F"Funny, kind, smart son"
