OL,6,FAzaan's parents were in court today.
OL,7,FAfter the hearing, they told ITV News
OL,8,Fthat they can't explain the loss they
OL,9,Ffeel at having lost their "funny,
OL,10,Fkind, smart son, who was everything to
OL,11,Fthem".
OL,13,FShazad Alam was given an interim
OL,14,Fdriving ban, and will be released on
OL,15,Fbail until he is sentenced on 21st
OL,16,FNovember.
OL,18,FThe judge warned Alam he was likely to
OL,19,Fbe sent to prison.
